<p>This is partly why I didn't want to make it part of the main article; I feel like there's not much else to go into, here. The primary reason I wrote it was to help show how the bugs could overcome a facility (by showing the bugs in action, and giving a sense of how dangerous they can be).</p>
<p>I'm a little leery of adding anything new, info-wise &#8212; I feel like adding much more might be showing too much. That being said, I'm open to ideas regarding how to flesh this out!</p>
<p><strong>EDIT:</strong> I suppose one solution is working to characterize the characters a little beforehand to create emotional investment &#8212; but I'm hesitant to do that, because they're basically just there to demonstrate how dangerous these things are.</p>

